wiki.summary: Line-up: Sabathan - lead vocals & bass Nornagest - lead guitar & vocals Nguaroth - lead guitar & vocals Glaurung - drums Recorded live in Porto Alegre, Brazil, at Bar Opinião on September 7th, 2004. Engineered by Treck and Dr. Feelgood Recorded by Sebastian (Hurricane Metal Studio) Mixed and mastered by Nguaroth and Nornagest "Eternal Misery" was recorded at the Dungeon. Engineered by S. Impens and Nguaroth Music by Enthroned Lyrics by Nornagest Read more on Last.fm.
